name: voucherEntryExportCSVFile

testSteps.description: Given that I'm logged in to Voucher Entry page

children.description: When i open page from sidebar menu: {Accounts Payable,Voucher Entries,Voucher Entry}

testSteps.description: Then the Payment Information form and its contents should show up
When I set the Supplier to '133339'
When I set the 'Invoice Number' to 'IHFqG6WYbi'
When I set the Currency to 'USD'
When i click on continue button
When I select the first Bank Account and click 'Submit' button if modal exist
When I set the Gross Amount to '15000'
When i click on continue button
Then the 'GL Distribution' form and its contents should show up

When I fill up the last row line and balance the amount using Account Number: '911000', Amount: <Previous balance amount>, Line Description: 'TEST', Employee: 'Taramarcaz', Cost Center: 'MAN5000', Gen Obj: 'AFGHAIGPREACT0', AOE: 'YAO-25005', Units: '10', Unit of Measure: '1' Project ID: 'F307'
When i click on export button
Then a file should be downloaded

Then the first GL Distribution CSV file first line should contain: Account Number: 'X.911000', Amount: <Previous balance amount>, Line Description: 'TEST', Employee: '31578', Cost Center: 'MAN5000', Gen Obj: 'AFGHAIGEACT0', AOE: 'YAO-25005', Purchase Order: ''', Units: '10', Unit of Measure: '1' Project ID: 'PJ000001', Line Ref: ''
Then the voucher entry successfully created modal and its contents should show up

title: Voucher entry export CSV file
